kind: llman.sdd.delta
ops[2]{op,req_id,title,statement,from,to,name}:
  add_requirement,r1,"snapshot-ops",System MUST support snapshot restore spawn list prune diff and merge operations on immutable session snapshots.,null,null,null
  add_requirement,r2,compaction,System MUST automatically compact context when conversation token count exceeds configured window threshold.,null,null,null
op_scenarios[2]{req_id,id,given,when,then}:
  r1,happy,a snapshot exists,spawn is called with snapshot_id and new prompt,new agent instance starts with inherited context from snapshot
  r2,happy,conversation exceeds 75% of context window,compaction is triggered,older turns are summarized and replaced with compact system message
